Hi,

STAThread can also be configured in the App.config file.
You have to set the following section:

  &lt;NUnit&gt;
    &lt;TestRunner&gt;
      &lt;!-- Valid values are STA,MTA. Others ignored. --&gt;
      &lt;add key=&quot;ApartmentState&quot; value=&quot;STA&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/TestRunner&gt;
  &lt;/NUnit&gt;

I have actually a working example with SpecFlow and WatiN. You can find the App.config of the project here:
http://gist.github.com/298113

We will publish some more SpecFlow samples soon.
Please notify us about problems or ask questions on the Google Group.

http://groups.google.com/group/specflow/

We would appreciate your feedback.

